entries.femaleVariant: Poverty might well be our lot, guv'nor, but order must be maintained.
Without order, man's but like a beast, ya feel me?
But Morty, I'm just... just... fuckin' hungry.
Hierarchy's inviolable, choom! Everyone's gotta know their place. Best bits go to Cataract Candy, I come second, you bring up the rear.
That ain't fair. Dude gives you the scop for free. We should all get the same.
Hey, if this arrangement ain't to your likin', you don't need to hang with us. Go on, see how you manage alone a while.
All right, don't need to hear that shit.
